issue.title: Resolve React issues... possibly switch from React to just JS, jQuery, AJAX?
issue.body:
I'm not sure how far @jaydurant was able to implement React in the frontend.  If it's not really doing us a lot of good, we could switch to a framework that is a little easier to work with and cleaner.  I've seen great and dynamic maps done without React or Angular or anything like that.

I'm really hoping to do a bunch of refactoring this week to get this up and running.  If React is really useful for us here, please chime in!  I'm not entirely clear on what it's doing specifically that cannot be accomplished without it currently.
